message.content: It is difficult to generalize the interests and obsessions of all kids in Somalia, as individual preferences can vary greatly. However, like kids in many other parts of the world, Somali children may be interested in various things such as technology, social media, sports, music, fashion, and entertainment. It is important to remember that Somalia is a diverse country with different cultural backgrounds and influences, so the interests of kids can also be shaped by their specific communities and environments.
